Class Person

java.lang.Object
Person
Direct Known Subclasses:
Customer
public abstract class Person
extends java.lang.Object
Instructor: Daniel Mejia, Course: CS 3331 Lab Assignment: Programming Assignment 4 Description: The purpose of the abstract class Person is to implement the attributes and methods that are common to every person involved in a banking system. Honesty Statement: We confirm that the work of this assignment is completely our own. By turning in this assignment, we declare that we did not receive unauthorized assistance. Moreover, all deliverables including, but not limited to the source code, lab report, and output files were written and produced by my partner and I, alone.
